    "description_long": "This is a compact green hatchback car with a rounded, aerodynamic body and four passenger doors. The car features dark-tinted windows, silver hubcaps on all four wheels, and black trim around the windows and along the lower body. The front end displays a pair of sleek headlights and a small grille, while the rear includes red taillights and a visible license plate. The side mirrors are color-matched to the body, and the car has a subtle roof curvature typical of hatchbacks. The overall design suggests a practical, urban-friendly vehicle with a rear hatch door for cargo access.",
